<bibRefCitation author="Csuzdi" box="[158,305,898,923]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" refString="Csuzdi, Cs. (2012) Earthworm species, a searchable database. Opuscula Zoologica, 43 (1), 97 - 99. Avaliable from: http: // earthworm. uw. hu / (Accessed 21 Jul. 2016)" type="journal article" year="2012">Csuzdi 2012</bibRefCitation>
